Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how data is handled when you use Extisma.One.

Data Collection
This bot may collect and temporarily store the following data:

Messages or commands sent to the bot for processing.
Usernames and IDs for bot functionality (e.g., logging or command responses).
Data Usage
Any collected data is used strictly for the operation of the bot.

No data is shared with third parties.
Logs, if any, are regularly cleared and are not permanently stored.
