Security
Reasonable measures are in place to ensure the security of any data handled by the bot. However, no system is 100% secure, and the owner cannot guarantee absolute protection.

Policy Changes
This policy may be updated at any time. Continued use of the bot constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
